synopsis.text: Nagai's beloved heroine, Honey Kisaragi, leads a double life as a typical high school beauty and the fiery, sword-wielding Cutey Honey. When her brilliant scientist father is abducted by the nefarious Panther Claw organization, Honey discovers a powerful device that allows her to transform into the heroine she was destined to become. In the 1997 film "Cutey Honey F," our quick-changing heroine embarks on a thrilling journey to a distant land, battling insect-like foes amidst a mesmerizing forest filled with radiant green butterflies. Alongside formidable adversaries like Beetle Mama and Lolita Crawler, Cutey Honey delves deeper into the secrets of South America. Prepare for a whimsical and action-packed adventure that showcases the more adorable side of Go Nagai's iconic franchise, appealing to both newcomers and longtime fans alike.
